# Changelog
## [1.2.1] - 2021-09-09
- Reformatted Fiber Color Guide from a text block to a 'key value' component.

children.text:
Tomorrow's Fiber Assignments

Step 1.

Verify that everyone that needs access to the fiber assignments is selected.

Step 2.

Wait for the script to finish to show the correct jobs.

Select all the rows (with the headings) located in the google sheet. Right click, then copy them.

Step 3.

Click the green E-Mail button to open an email with everything filled out.

Step 4.

Paste Jobs in the body of the E-Mail and click Send.
